{"id": "art-70", "label": "Art. 70", "title": "Art. 70: Procedura de soluţionare a abţinerii sau a recuzării procurorului", "slug": "art-70", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_432494497\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2677\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_432494497\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 70:\nProcedura de solu&#355;ionare a ab&#355;inerii sau a recuz&#259;rii\nprocurorului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_209975970\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2676\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_209975970\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, asupra ab&#355;inerii\nsau recuz&#259;rii procurorului se pronun&#355;&#259; procurorul ierarhic\nsuperior. Declara&#355;ia de ab&#355;inere sau cererea de recuzare se\nadreseaz&#259; acestuia, sub sanc&#355;iunea inadmisibilit&#259;&#355;ii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_42347613\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2675\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_42347613\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Inadmisibilitatea se constat&#259; de procurorul în\nfa&#355;a c&#259;ruia s-a formulat cererea de recuzare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_910176135\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2674\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_910176135\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Procurorul ierarhic superior solu&#355;ioneaz&#259;\ncererea în 48 de ore, prin ordonan&#355;&#259; care nu este supus&#259;\nniciunei c&#259;i de atac.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1009955050\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2673\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1009955050\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, procurorul recuzat\npoate participa la solu&#355;ionarea cererii privitoare la m&#259;sura\npreventiv&#259; &#351;i poate efectua acte sau dispune orice m&#259;suri care\njustific&#259; urgen&#355;a.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1941496231\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2672\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1941496231\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazul declara&#355;iei de ab&#355;inere,\ndispozi&#355;iile alin. (3) &#351;i (4) se aplic&#259; în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_182190006\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2671\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_182190006\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În caz de admitere a ab&#355;inerii sau a\nrecuz&#259;rii, procurorul ierarhic superior stabile&#351;te în ce\nm&#259;sur&#259; actele îndeplinite ori m&#259;surile dispuse se men&#355;in.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1993111360\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2670\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1993111360\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Atunci când procedura se desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; în\nfa&#355;a judec&#259;torului de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i, a\njudec&#259;torului de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; sau a instan&#355;ei de\njudecat&#259;, declara&#355;ia de ab&#355;inere sau cererea de recuzare a\nprocurorului care particip&#259; la &#351;edin&#355;a de judecat&#259; se\nadreseaz&#259; acestora, sub sanc&#355;iunea inadmisibilit&#259;&#355;ii.\nInadmisibilitatea se constat&#259; de judec&#259;torul sau, dup&#259; caz, de\ncompletul de judecat&#259; în fa&#355;a c&#259;ruia s-a formulat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_509399603\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2669\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_509399603\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Ab&#355;inerea sau recuzarea procurorului care\nparticip&#259; la &#351;edin&#355;a de judecat&#259; se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259;\nde judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i, judec&#259;torul\nde camer&#259; preliminar&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz, de completul de\njudecat&#259; în fa&#355;a c&#259;ruia a fost ridicat&#259;, în camera de\nconsiliu, în cel mult 24 de ore. Dac&#259; se apreciaz&#259; necesar pentru\nsolu&#355;ionarea cererii, se pot efectua orice verific&#259;ri &#351;i pot fi\nasculta&#355;i subiec&#355;ii procesuali principali, p&#259;r&#355;ile &#351;i\nprocurorul care se ab&#355;ine sau a c&#259;rui recuzare se solicit&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1784182177\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2668\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1784182177\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)În caz de admitere a ab&#355;inerii sau a recuz&#259;rii\nprocurorului care particip&#259; la &#351;edin&#355;a de judecat&#259;,\njudec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i, judec&#259;torul de\ncamer&#259; preliminar&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz, completul de judecat&#259; va\nstabili în ce m&#259;sur&#259; actele îndeplinite ori m&#259;surile dispuse se\nmen&#355;in.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1487130202\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2667\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1487130202\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Încheierea prin care se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259;\nab&#355;inerea ori recuzarea nu este supus&#259; niciunei c&#259;i de atac.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}